69
00:07:25.520 --> 00:07:26.567
Uh. yes.

70
00:07:26.680 --> 00:07:28.444
Yeah. 'cause you're like.
"Oh. fuck. I'm in
someone else's house.

71
00:07:28.520 --> 00:07:29.806
"Can I do this.
can I do that?"

72
00:07:29.880 --> 00:07:31.928
And this card.
it just takes
all that worry away.

73
