93
00:08:27.600 --> 00:08:29.602
It's not cozy.
it's claustrophobic.

94
00:08:29.680 --> 00:08:31.409
No. No way. I wasn't
thinking that.

95
00:08:31.480 --> 00:08:34.086
I was thinking.
"This is really cool."

96
00:08:35.080 --> 00:08:38.766
Caleb. there's a reason there
are no windows in this room.

97
00:08:38.880 --> 00:08:40.211
There is?
Uh-huh.

98
00:08:40.920 --> 00:08:42.524
This building isn't a house.

99
00:08:42.600 --> 00:08:44.602
It's a research facility.

100
00:08:45.440 --> 00:08:47.681
Buried in these walls
is enough fiber optic cable

101
00:08:47.760 --> 00:08:50.127
