111
00:09:20.800 --> 00:09:22.245
"to confirm that
no disclosure

112
00:09:22.320 --> 00:09:24.527
"of information
has taken place

113
00:09:24.600 --> 00:09:26.841
"in public
or private forums.

114
00:09:27.240 --> 00:09:29.242
"using any means
of communication.

115
00:09:29.320 --> 00:09:31.084
"including but not limited

116
00:09:31.160 --> 00:09:33.242
"to that which is
disclosed orally

117
00:09:34.040 --> 00:09:36.520
"or in written
or electronic form."

118
00:09:39.640 --> 00:09:40.766
I think I need a lawyer.

119
00:09:40.840 --> 00:09:43.923
It's standard.
It doesn't feel very standard.

120
00:09:44.160 --> 00:09:45.924
Okay. it's not standard.

121
00:09:46.000 --> 00:09:48.765
What can I tell you. Caleb?
You don't have to sign it.

122
00:09:48.840 --> 00:09:50.285
You know. we can spend
the next few days

123
