151
00:12:58.920 --> 00:12:59.921
Hello.

152
00:13:02.480 --> 00:13:03.481
Hi.

153
00:13:05.160 --> 00:13:06.491
I'm Caleb.

154
00:13:08.600 --> 00:13:10.045
Hello. Caleb.

155
00:13:12.680 --> 00:13:14.205
