292
00:22:50.680 --> 00:22:52.330
So I came to see
what's going on.

293
00:22:52.400 --> 00:22:54.050
The power cuts. yeah.

294
00:22:54.120 --> 00:22:57.329
We've been getting
those recently. Um...

295
00:22:59.240 --> 00:23:00.924
