Hit me.

315
00:24:41.880 --> 00:24:43.882
Yeah. well. I'm not sure.

316
00:24:44.400 --> 00:24:47.324
I'm still trying to.
uh. figure
the examination formats.

317
00:24:47.400 --> 00:24:48.686
Uh-huh.

318
00:24:48.760 --> 00:24:50.524
Yeah. it feels like

319
00:24:50.720 --> 00:24:54.441
testing Ava through conversation
is kind of a closed loop.

320
00:24:54.720 --> 00:24:56.404
It's a closed loop?
Yeah.

321
00:24:56.480 --> 00:24:58.369
Like testing
a chess computer

322
00:24:58.440 --> 00:25:00.329
by only playing chess.

323
00:25:00.840 --> 00:25:03.491
How else do you test
a chess computer?

324
00:25:04.200 --> 00:25:05.611
Well. it depends.

325
00:25:05.680 --> 00:25:07.808
You know. I mean.
you can play it

326
