Our conversations
are one-sided.

360
00:27:12.640 --> 00:27:16.008
You ask circumspect questions
and study my responses.

361
00:27:17.720 --> 00:27:18.721
Yes.

362
00:27:18.800 --> 00:27:20.484
You learn about me

363
