My friend?

427
00:30:14.280 --> 00:30:15.611
I... Yeah. I hope so.

428
00:30:15.680 --> 00:30:17.205
A good friend?

429
00:30:17.480 --> 00:30:19.164
CALEB: Um. yeah.

430
00:30:19.240 --> 00:30:20.960
Well. no. no. no.
I mean. not a good friend.

431
00:30:21.000 --> 00:30:23.162
A good friend is. uh...

432
00:30:23.240 --> 00:30:25.925
We only just met
each other. you know.

433
00:30:26.080 --> 00:30:28.686
So it takes time
to be able to. um...

434
00:30:29.400 --> 00:30:31.607
To get to know
each other. I guess.
(ALARM BLARING)

435
00:30:31.680 --> 00:30:34.365
FEMALE AUTOMATED VOICE:
<i>Power cut.
Backup power activated.</i>

436
00:30:54.720 --> 00:30:55.846
Caleb.

437
00:31:02.680 --> 00:31:04.205
You're wrong.

