445
00:31:28.680 --> 00:31:31.331
You shouldn't trust
anything he says.

446
00:31:34.960 --> 00:31:36.530
FEMALE AUTOMATED VOICE:
<i>Power restored.</i>

447
00:31:37.640 --> 00:31:38.926
And if we made
a list of books

448
00:31:39.040 --> 00:31:40.849
