basis of a discussion.
(CHIMES)

450
00:31:44.960 --> 00:31:46.450
Is that okay?

451
00:31:48.480 --> 00:31:49.641
Caleb?

452
00:31:51.000 --> 00:31:52.047
Mmm-hmm.

453
00:31:52.120 --> 00:31:53.121
Yeah.

454
00:31:55.440 --> 00:31:56.566
