455
00:32:02.480 --> 00:32:03.527
CALEB: Thank you.

456
00:32:05.280 --> 00:32:07.647
Oh. shit! Are you
fucking kidding me?

457
00:32:08.520 --> 00:32:10.329
Did it get on you?
No. no. it's. uh...

458
00:32:11.080 --> 00:32:12.081
It's all right.
I got it.

459
00:32:12.320 --> 00:32:13.651
Dude. you're wasting
your time talking to her.

460
00:32:13.720 --> 00:32:15.960
She doesn't understand English.
Just give her the napkin.

461
00:32:18.280 --> 00:32:19.486
Sorry.

462
