It's like a firewall
against leaks.

463
00:32:22.360 --> 00:32:24.044
It means I can talk
trade secrets over dinner

464
00:32:24.120 --> 00:32:26.202
and know
it'll go no further.

465
00:32:26.280 --> 00:32:27.691
It also means that
I can't tell her that

466
00:32:27.760 --> 00:32:29.489
I'm pissed when she's
so fucking clumsy

467
00:32:29.560 --> 00:32:31.449
