that you're pissed.

469
00:32:33.560 --> 00:32:35.927
Yeah? Good.
Because I am pissed.

470
00:32:36.520 --> 00:32:37.885
Hey. Kyoko.

471
00:32:38.360 --> 00:32:39.600
Go-go.

472
00:32:48.320 --> 00:32:49.685
It's funny.

473
00:32:50.040 --> 00:32:51.326
You know.

474
