installed it fucked something up.

486
00:33:20.120 --> 00:33:21.770
Can't you just get them
to come back?

487
00:33:22.080 --> 00:33:24.162
No. There's too much
classified stuff here.

488
00:33:24.240 --> 00:33:26.766
So after the job was done.
I just had them all killed.

489
00:33:31.800 --> 00:33:32.847
Anyway.

490
00:33:32.920 --> 00:33:35.048
Here's to your
second day. buddy.

491
00:33:36.880 --> 00:33:38.120
Cheers.

492
00:33:38.400 --> 00:33:39.606
Cheers.

493
00:33:42.600 --> 00:33:45.570
So how did it go?
What do you have to report?

494
00:33:48.240 --> 00:33:50.891
You saw how the day went.
didn't you?

495
00:33:52.240 --> 00:33:54.129
I mean. I assume
you're. uh.

496
00:33:54.400 --> 00:33:56.050
