497
00:33:56.120 --> 00:33:58.964
Sure. But I want to
hear your take on it.

498
00:34:01.400 --> 00:34:05.564
Yeah. there was one interesting
thing that happened with Ava today.

499
00:34:09.040 --> 00:34:10.041
Yeah?
Yeah.

500
00:34:13.480 --> 00:34:15.084
She made a joke.

501
00:34:17.280 --> 00:34:20.523
Right. When she threw
your line back at you. (CHUCKLES)

502
00:34:21.200 --> 00:34:23.726
About being interested
to see what she'd choose.

503
00:34:23.800 --> 00:34:25.040
Yeah. I noticed that. too.

504
00:34:25.120 --> 00:34:27.691
Yeah. and it got me
thinking. it's. uh...

505
00:34:28.680 --> 00:34:30.603
In a way.
it's the best
indication of Al

506
00:34:30.680 --> 00:34:32.762
that I've seen
in her so far.

507
00:34:32.880 --> 00:34:35.042
It's discretely complicated.

508
00:34:35.480 --> 00:34:38.211
It's like. um...
It's kind of non-autistic.

509
00:34:38.560 --> 00:34:39.925
What do you mean?

510
00:34:40.440 --> 00:34:42.010
She could only do that
with an awareness

511
00:34:42.080 --> 00:34:44.003
of her own mind.

512
00:34:45.280 --> 00:34:46.645
and also
an awareness of mine.

513
00:34:46.760 --> 00:34:49.161
Oh. she's aware of you all right.
(CHUCKLES)

514
00:34:52.360 --> 00:34:53.850
And what about
the power cut?

515
00:34:57.080 --> 00:34:58.969
Sorry?
The power cut.

516
00:35:00.440 --> 00:35:01.960
It's the only part
that I couldn't see.

517
00:35:02.000 --> 00:35:04.651
Cameras fail.
I lose audio. the works.

518
00:35:07.280 --> 00:35:08.884
So what happened?

519
00:35:13.400 --> 00:35:14.686
Nothing.

520
00:35:14.920 --> 00:35:18.481
Nothing? She didn't
remark on it at all?

521
00:35:22.760 --> 00:35:23.841
No.

522
